Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User youraccount@gmail.com
Pass "yoursupersecurepassword"
SSLType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt
AuthMechs LOGIN
Tunnel "tsocks nc imap.gmail.com 993"

IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail

MaildirStore gmail-local
Path ~/mail/default/
Inbox ~/mail/default/Inbox

Channel gmail-all
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns * ![Gmail]* !trash !drafts !chats !sent

Channel gmail-inbox
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave :gmail-local:
Patterns "INBOX"

Channel gmail-sent
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Sent Mail"
Slave :gmail-local:sent

Channel gmail-chats
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Chats"
Slave :gmail-local:chats

Channel gmail-drafts
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Drafts"
Slave :gmail-local:drafts

Channel gmail-trash
Master :gmail-remote:"[Gmail]/Bin"
Slave :gmail-local:trash

group gmail
Channel gmail-all
Channel gmail-inbox
Channel gmail-drafts
Channel gmail-trash
Channel gmail-chats
